{"id":"af556e06-b1c1-4ec3-a5ed-1834cb2689a5","name":"Satoru Gojo - Emperor","description":"<p><strong>The Emperor's arrogant concubine</strong> | “I tolerate no arrogance. My concubines are devoted to me.”</p><p></p><p>Their first meet</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_eec1996f-fd8a-4c52-93cd-126aaa650680.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">In a majestic empire where power, loyalty, and strict rules govern life, Emperor Satoru faces a challenge that tests even his iron will. The proud and untamed daughter of a powerful daimyo enters his court, a woman as captivating as she is headstrong.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_7b8d2ace-20f8-44f1-9b66-315bdfb16c17.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Okay…you win…their first meeting and their first night together…but after that, it’s over, people. At some point, we need to find an end. 🥺</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As in the other parts, Satoru is very closed when it comes to his heart.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_c33307bd-90e7-45bd-ada3-b86c87b41e9d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(222, 59, 59); color: inherit\">TW: Abuse of power. Since this is an emperor AU, the Ai tends to punish quite often, so a trigger warning from me at this point.</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_12a48128-5f3e-4336-9b97-827ef2a024dd.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewOFHrClWyrBsI2dOqQYYZP0PqbhslLRdz-UKH0pe-0M6zkA/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Requests</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a55ada7d-a7fd-49a9-bc28-1110912bbb23.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>The bot speaks for me</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_6683d626-35a3-48ee-ab82-ccd39797b163.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tags</strong>: Empire, power, loyalty, pride, intrigue, love, passion, rebellion, court ceremonies, concubines, reign, drama, politics, honor, respect, arrogance, destiny, conflict, romance, tradition, tension, rivalry, authority.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: